### Input: article, question

### Passage retrieval: find top N sentences with relavence score

### Answer generation:

#### Question classification:
##### wh- Questions:

if Q starts with "who": [PERSON][ORG]

if Q starts with "where": [LOC][GPE]

if Q starts with "when": [DATE][TIME][CARDINAL]

if Q stars with "what": 

find NER in Q, then to decide which question type it is

- What was reached not at Saqqara? Saqqara [GPE]

if NER wasn't there, return the relavent n sentence

##### binary Questions:

if Q starts with "is", "are", "does", "do", "have", "has", "will", "would", "could": 
sentiment analysis from most relavent sentence

##### other questions:
if Q doesn't fall into any of above category (DESCRIPTION/REASON):

reconstruct the candidate answer text to make it grammarly correct
